The paper deals with a computational problem related to signal processing and image analysis, specifically the crystallographic phase retrieval problem. This problem is related to the recovery of a signal from its Fourier magnitude or periodic auto-correlation. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
